## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cbe35-102">Il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> proprietà determinano come gli utenti possono selezionare elementi in un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cbe35-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> properties together determine how users can select items in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cbe35-103">Ad esempio, se il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> è singola e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> è <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit>, l'utente può selezionare una cella in una fase nel <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit.Cell>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cbe35-103">For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> is Single and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> is <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit>, the user can select one cell at a time in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit.Cell>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cbe35-104">Modalità inExtended, selezionare più elementi tenendo premuto il tasto MAIUSC per estendere la selezione da un punto di ancoraggio o i tasti CTRL tasto singolarmente per selezionare elementi aggiuntivi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cbe35-104">InExtended mode, select multiple items by holding down the SHIFT key to extend the selection from an anchor point or the CTRL key to individually select additional items.</span></span>  
  
